	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64563087">It is also the case that fossil fuels are also polluting. We don't see buildings covered in black soot so much any more but we know that both petrol and diesel produce particles that are potentially carcinogenic and noxious gases that can cause breathing difficulties. Clean air acts and low emission zones help in areas particularly badly affected but it would be great if the whole planet was a low emission zone.  If you ask me, there really are very few downsides to renewable energy.</div>
