		<div id="comment_body_64563171"><p>You are way out of date. These are not simple single events like a dice roll. They're complex events with lots of data attached to them, and scientists are now at the state of being able to attribute the degree to which climate change has caused particular weather events. You think of this as in-principle impossible, but you're just wrong.</p><p>Here: <a href="https://www.worldweatherattribution.org/" title="worldweath...bution.org">https://www.worldweatherattrib...</a> [worldweath...bution.org]</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64563171">

